\n\r\nYou want a website that is <em>unique</em> to you or your business, so you stand out from the crowd. You want a website that is <em>user-friendly</em> and easily conveys the information you need to share. But you dont know where to start, and you dont want to go it alone. Let me help!\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">If you are a business seeking a web presence or an employer looking to hire you can get in touch with me here.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">Hi, my name is </span><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">Natalie Rose</span><span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">. I</span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Develop and customize sites for individuals and businesses.</li>\r\n 	<li>Build custom themes or customize existing WordPress themes, depending on your needsand budget.</li>\r\n 	<li>Bring expertise in responsive design, so your site will look great on everydevice that accesses it.</li>\r\n 	<li>I convert designs to high-performance code whilst respecting your designers compositions.</li>\r\n 	<li>Handle site transfers.</li>\r\n 	<li>Build custom email templates</li>\r\n 	<li></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">Front-end development</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, JQuery, Responsive design.</span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">I create responsive websites that allow the user to experience your website in the best and most appropriate way suited to the device they are using. I convert designs to high-performance code whilst respecting your designers compositions.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">WordPress Development</span>\r\n\r\nThemes, admin/plugin setup, custom functionality\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-indent: 0em;\">In many projects, clients require the ability to manage the content of their website. To do this, I integrate front-end templates into WordPress themes and offer custom functionality via PHP.</span>\r\n\r\n&nbsp;